Do you understand?

869
00:41:27,600 --> 00:41:28,950
Facing the suffering of the people,

870
00:41:29,390 --> 00:41:30,950
you just choose to stand by?

871
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:32,120
This is a crucial moment.

872
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:32,710
As the Governor,

873
00:41:32,710 --> 00:41:33,470
you have the authority
to use military grain

874
00:41:33,470 --> 00:41:34,280
to stabilize the home front.

875
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,670
That's silly.

876
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:38,000
Go back to your room.

877
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:39,710
Go back.

878
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:47,430
So stubborn.

879
00:41:58,120 --> 00:41:58,910
Young Master.

880
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:01,280
These dishes have been heated
several times.

881
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,520
Please eat some.

882
00:42:02,670 --> 00:42:03,280
If you don't eat,

883
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,870
you won't have the energy
to pursue Miss Luo.

884
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:05,670
Get out.

885
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:09,430
Young Master, please eat some.

886
00:42:09,870 --> 00:42:11,800
Get out.

887
00:42:33,710 --> 00:42:35,230
Mr. Yanjin, we're ready.

888
00:42:35,470 --> 00:42:36,230
Lian Qi,

889
00:42:36,950 --> 00:42:38,360
you don't have to go with me this time.

890
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:39,870
Why?

891
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,760
I trust you the most.

892
00:42:46,230 --> 00:42:46,910
You need to help me

893
00:42:48,950 --> 00:42:50,230
